headline: Christian Mumenthaler Named to MetLife’s Board of Directors
summary: NEW YORK, February 26, 2025--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that Christian Mumenthaler has been elected to its board of directors, effective May 1, 2025.
